fitcurve.name: fit_name
fitcurve.documentation: A name of the fit (user selectable).

fitcurve.name: fit_equation
fitcurve.documentation: A string equation of the fit in the form y=f(x).

fitcurve.name: fit_parameters
fitcurve.documentation: The values of the fit parameters.

fitcurve.name: fit_parameter_names
fitcurve.documentation: The names of the fit variables (should correspond to variables in the fit_equation)

fitcurve.name: fit_independent_variable_names
fitcurve.documentation: The name(s) of the independent variable(s)

fitcurve.name: fit_dependent_variable_names
fitcurve.documentation: The name(s) of the dependent variable(s)

fitcurve.name: fit_sse
fitcurve.documentation: The name(s) of the dependent variable(s)

fitcurve.name: fit_constraints
fitcurve.documentation: A structure with fields fit_constraint_name and fit_constraint_value

fitcurve.name: fit_data
fitcurve.documentation: A structure with fields input_data_field, output_data_field, output_number_examples
